OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772697874
OL,3,CParents, teachers, and pupils protest
OL,4,Cagainst performing arts school closure
OL,6,FA protest has taken place in Liverpool
OL,7,Fagainst plans to close a performing
OL,8,Farts school in the summer.
OL,10,FTeachers, parents and pupils at the
OL,11,FLiverpool Institute for Performing
OL,12,FArts were told on Friday 27 February
OL,13,Fthat the school will shut down at the
OL,14,Fend of the academic year.
OL,16,FThe school which opened in 2014 is for
OL,17,Fchildren from four to 16 and is not
OL,18,Fconnected to the college of the same
OL,19,Fname founded by Sir Paul McCartney.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
