PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772697874
OL,3,CParents, teachers, and pupils protest
OL,4,Cagainst performing arts school closure
OL,6,FThe school faces a financial deficit,
OL,7,Ffalling pupil numbers and in its most
OL,8,Frecent OFSTED report it was rated
OL,9,Finadequate but teachers and parents
OL,10,Fsay many improvements have been made
OL,11,Fsince then.
OL,13,FA Department for Education
OL,14,Fspokesperson said:"We have taken the
OL,15,Fdifficult decision to close Liverpool
OL,16,FInstitute of Performing Arts (LIPA)
OL,17,FSchool by mutual consent.
OL,26,@vD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772697874
OL,3,CParents, teachers, and pupils protest
OL,4,Cagainst performing arts school closure
OL,6,F"The decision to close any school is
OL,7,Fnot taken lightly. Declining pupil
OL,8,Fnumbers and the school's unsustainable
OL,9,Ffinancial position has made it
OL,10,Fchallenging for the trust to continue
OL,11,Fto provide an environment that offers
OL,12,Fa high-quality education.
OL,14,F"We understand the closure of the
OL,15,Fschool is a matter of concern for the
OL,16,Fcommunity. The trust and Liverpool
OL,17,FCity Council will offer their full
OL,18,Fsupport to parents while they work to
OL,19,Ffind suitable alternative schools for
OL,20,Fpupils."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
