PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772697874
OL,3,CParents, teachers, and pupils protest
OL,4,Cagainst performing arts school closure
OL,6,FAnna Mullholland's 15-year-old
OL,7,Fdaughter has been at the school since
OL,8,Fshe was four, she says news of the
OL,9,Fclosure was a bolt from the blue: "My
OL,10,Fdaughter left the school, as normal,
OL,11,Fon a Friday, and then by five past
OL,12,Fnine, we've had an email saying school
OL,13,Fwas going to close, and the emails
OL,14,Fmade it seem very final.
OL,16,F"Overwhelmingly, her experience has
OL,17,Fbeen good, especially in recent years,
OL,18,Fshe's got stability from this school. "
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772697874
OL,3,CParents, teachers, and pupils protest
OL,4,Cagainst performing arts school closure
OL,6,F"She's thriving, she's happy. She's
OL,7,Fjust had some amazing mock results and
OL,8,Fshe's got great predictive grades for
OL,9,FGCSEs.
OL,11,FAnna says the decision to close has
OL,12,Fcome from the Board of Trustees but
OL,13,Fshe hopes the strength of feeling will
OL,14,Fchange their minds. She said: "Please
OL,15,Flisten to the parents, please listen
OL,16,Fto the children., please listen to the
OL,17,Fstaff.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772697874
OL,3,CParents, teachers, and pupils protest
OL,4,Cagainst performing arts school closure
OL,6,F"There's so much support for the
OL,7,Fschool, We are an unusual provision.
OL,8,FThere's nothing else around in
OL,9,FLiverpool like us.
OL,11,FKatie Brennan is a teacher at LIPA,
OL,12,Fand she said news of the proposed
OL,13,Fclosure has come as a shock.: "All
OL,14,Fstaff were told on Friday morning, in
OL,15,Fa special briefing, where a statement
OL,16,Fwas read to us by our executive head
OL,17,Fteacher. And it came as a complete
OL,18,Fshock to all of us. And it was a very
OL,19,Fdifficult day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772697874
OL,3,CParents, teachers, and pupils protest
OL,4,Cagainst performing arts school closure
OL,6,F"These people that make the decisions
OL,7,Fhaven't been walking the classrooms,
OL,8,Fthey haven't been down the corridors,
OL,9,Fthey haven't been there at play times.
OL,11,F"They don't see what we are doing on a
OL,12,Fgranular level every single day, and
OL,13,Fthe difference that we're making to
OL,14,Fthese children, these families' lives.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772697874
OL,3,CParents, teachers, and pupils protest
OL,4,Cagainst performing arts school closure
OL,6,F"Everything we do is channelled
OL,7,Fthrough the creative and the
OL,8,Fperforming arts, whether that's the
OL,9,Fway we approach math investigations,
OL,10,Fwhether that's in drama lessons, we
OL,11,Ffocus on, you know, building well-
OL,12,Frounded children that are able to
OL,13,Fspeak for themselves, articulate their
OL,14,Fideas.
OL,16,F"It's not just about dancing on cars
OL,17,Fdown Hope Street. It's about using the
OL,18,Fcreativity and the performance that's
OL,19,Fso rich in our city. to enhance
OL,20,Feducation and enrich it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
