PN,39509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772697874
OL,3,CParents, teachers, and pupils protest
OL,4,Cagainst performing arts school closure
OL,6,F"We've got the most amazing cultural
OL,7,Fneighbours on our doorstep. We're
OL,8,Faround the corner from the Everyman,
OL,9,Fthe Philharmonic, we're so uniquely
OL,10,Fplaced, and the staff are all really
OL,11,Fpassionate about how we teach our
OL,12,Fcurriculum. "
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
