CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772697874
OL,3,CParents, teachers, and pupils protest
OL,4,Cagainst performing arts school closure
OL,6,FAva is studying for her GCSEs at the
OL,7,Fschool and is heartbroken at the
OL,8,Fthought of leaving, she said: "I've
OL,9,Fbeen here since reception, so about 10
OL,10,Fyears, and we're all so close
OL,11,Ftogether, and we've been, like,
OL,12,Fstudying so hard for our GCSEs, and
OL,13,Fwe're halfway through this year, so
OL,14,Fit'd be horrible to leave now. "
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
