PN,39511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772697874
OL,3,CParents, teachers, and pupils protest
OL,4,Cagainst performing arts school closure
OL,6,FA Liverpool City Council spokesperson,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are aware of the decision by
OL,8,Fthe Department for Education and the
OL,9,FBoard of Trustees at the Liverpool
OL,10,FInstitute of Performing Arts (LIPA)
OL,11,FSchool to enter a listening period
OL,12,Fahead of closing the school from 31
OL,13,FAugust 2026.
OL,15,F"Our role now as the Local Authority
OL,16,Fis to find suitable alternative school
OL,17,Fplaces for affected children and young
OL,18,Fpeople and have been working with the
OL,19,FLIPA Multi-Academy Trust and the
OL,20,FDepartment for Education on this issue.
OL,26,@oD@GOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772697874
OL,3,CParents, teachers, and pupils protest
OL,4,Cagainst performing arts school closure
OL,6,F"If a Year 6 child has selected to
OL,7,Fcontinue their education with LIPA
OL,8,FSchool into the Secondary phase they
OL,9,Fwill not be allocated a place at LIPA
OL,10,FSchool. However, every child will
OL,11,Freceive an offer of a secondary school
OL,12,Fplace.
OL,14,F"There's a wide range of school
OL,15,Fadmissions information and guidance on
OL,16,Fthe city council website and the
OL,17,Fschool admissions team will be on hand
OL,18,Fto provide information and support to
OL,19,Faffected families."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
