OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772697874
OL,3,CParents, teachers, and pupils protest
OL,4,Cagainst performing arts school closure
OL,6,FThere is now a four week consultation
OL,7,Fperiod and everyone involved in the
OL,8,Fprotest is determined to keep up the
OL,9,Ffight to save their school.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
